Statistics

   Population: 267,954,764 (July 1997 est.)  ^1

   GDP 1996: $7.61 trillion (1996 est.) ^2

   R&D as a percent of GDP = 2.55% ^3


   National R&D Effort 1996: ^4

     $193 billion
     * 32.5% of which was supported by the public sector
     * 62.7% of which was supported by the private sector

   National Energy R&D Effort 1996:

     $4.4 billion ^a
     * 43.6% of which was supported by the private sector
     * 56.4% of which is supported by the public sector


